FBIS4-8131 "dreeu069_b_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-069 Daily Report 8 Apr 1994 BULGARIA Berov Discharged, Declared `Fit for Work' Berov Discharged, Declared `Fit for Work' AU0804170094 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1600 GMT 8 Apr 94 AU0804170094 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network Bulgarian BFN [Text] Today the group of consultants treating Prime Minister Lyuben Berov decided to discharge the prime minister from the hospital because his hospital treatment has been successfully concluded. The condition of the prime minister's cardiovascular system has been stabilized, and it is the view of the consultants that the prime minister is fit for work.
